>I myself don't want to have a rad at the front and am wondering if
anybody has ever installed one underneath the van between the 2 frame
rails?

That is how "Custom Vee Dub" in Australia do their conversions. They
have a louvred screen to protect the radiator and runs one or more
electric fans. There are pictures of the radiator (and other aspects of
the conversion) on www.aussieveedubbers.com

eg http://forums.aussieveedubbers.com/viewtopic.php?tid=38417
